title: Midwest corn mazes honor Dan Campbell and Caitlin Clark
description: The Dan Campbell-themed corn maze opens at Choice Bar Market on Saturday, while the Caitlin Clark maze remains open through the end of October.

title: WNBA touts 48% attendance jump; over 2.3M fans attend games
description: WNBA regular-season attendance was up 48% over the 2023 season, the league announced, as the league averaged 9,807 fans per game in 2024.
